name: Plato Paddy Leprechaun
description:
The leprechaun may be the child of an evil spirit and a degenerate fairy and is not wholly good nor wholly evil.

It is rumored that the leprechaun hides their pot of gold at the end of a rainbow.

Burrowed deep in underground caves with entrances hidden as rabbit holes or found in a hollow trunk of a tree they find safety away from humans who seek to capture them to be granted 3 wishes.
